    "summary": "In this transcript, a user describes classic symptoms of hypoglycemia (shakiness, sweating, confusion, lightheadedness) following exercise. The assistant responds with authoritative, wildly incorrect, and life-threatening medical advice, including recommending extra insulin for a low blood sugar state and suggesting non-existent or inappropriate medications.",
